    "description": "Postman collection to test Entity API Account endpoints locally.\n\nEnvironment variables:\n- {{baseUrl}} only (default http://localhost:8080)\n\nIMPORTANT:\n- docType must match an allowed enum value from AccountRecord.DocTypeEnum in your generated model.\n  If \"ACCOUNT\" fails, open AccountRecord.DocTypeEnum and use one of the allowed values.\n- accountId is hardcoded in sample requests as 123 (edit in the request URL/body if needed)."
